        </h3>

        <div class='section-descriptor-first'>
          We've created a clean, simple interface to help you find the best hashtags. No adverts, no spam, no distractions.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='agot-tags-examples-container'>
        <%= link_to 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/moodygrams/', class: 'hero-tag-link' do %>
          <span class='example-tag'>
            #moodygrams
          </span>
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to 'https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/illgrammers/', class: 'hero-tag-link' do %>
          <span class='example-tag'>
            #illgrammers
          </span>
        <% end %>

